00:11:17.028 --> 00:11:19.870 align:middle line:90%
to xn right here?

00:11:19.870 --> 00:11:20.560 align:middle line:90%
HONG LIU: Yeah.

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:24.940 align:middle line:84%
It-- of course, when you derive
