00:11:24.940 --> 00:11:27.200 align:middle line:84%
for this argument,
it doesn't matter.

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:30.200 align:middle line:90%
It just has to act to the right.

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:34.250 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, for the initial state,
you have to act to the right.

00:11:34.250 --> 00:11:36.530 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, of course, to
derive that theorem,

00:11:36.530 --> 00:11:37.991 align:middle line:90%
the time-order matters.

00:11:37.991 --> 00:11:38.491 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:11:38.491 --> 00:11:42.640 align:middle line:90%


00:11:42.640 --> 00:11:43.277 align:middle line:90%
Yes?

