HONG LIU: Yeah, yeah.

01:00:40.640 --> 01:00:43.140 align:middle line:84%
I will talk about things related
to this a little bit later.

01:00:43.140 --> 01:00:43.640 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

01:00:43.640 --> 01:00:47.880 align:middle line:90%


01:00:47.880 --> 01:00:48.870 align:middle line:90%
Good?

01:00:48.870 --> 01:00:51.390 align:middle line:84%
And then we can write
down explicit solutions

01:00:51.390 --> 01:00:54.360 align:middle line:84%
for those gammas, so
that's two representations.

01:00:54.360 --> 01:00:57.060 align:middle line:84%
From those solutions
of beta and alpha,

01:00:57.060 --> 01:01:01.030 align:middle line:84%
we can write down different
solutions of gamma.

01:01:01.030 --> 01:01:08.650 align:middle line:84%
So for example, for 1, you're
corresponding to gamma 0 equal

01:01:08.650 --> 01:01:10.330 align:middle line:90%
to minus i.

01:01:10.330 --> 01:01:16.420 align:middle line:84%
So now this is minus i times a
2-by-2 matrix, OK, or i, 0, 0,

01:01:16.420 --> 01:01:24.660 align:middle line:84%
minus i, OK, and the gamma i
is equal to 0, minus sigma i,

01:01:24.660 --> 01:01:29.250 align:middle line:90%
minus i sigma i, 0.

01:01:29.250 --> 01:01:31.170 align:middle line:84%
And the second solution
there corresponding

01:01:31.170 --> 01:01:42.040 align:middle line:84%
to gamma 0 equal to 0, i, i, 0,
and then gamma i equal to 0--

01:01:42.040 --> 01:01:45.200 align:middle line:90%


01:01:45.200 --> 01:01:52.170 align:middle line:84%
I think it's also minus
i sigma i, i sigma i, 0.

01:01:52.170 --> 01:01:52.670 align:middle line:90%
OK.

01:01:52.670 --> 01:01:56.880 align:middle line:90%


01:01:56.880 --> 01:01:59.940 align:middle line:84%
Good, so these are just--
again, these are just good--

01:01:59.940 --> 01:02:02.070 align:middle line:84%
so these are two
different representations

01:02:02.070 --> 01:02:03.316 align:middle line:90%
of this algebra.

01:02:03.316 --> 01:02:03.816 align:middle line:90%
OK.

01:02:03.816 --> 01:02:06.990 align:middle line:90%


01:02:06.990 --> 01:02:08.940 align:middle line:90%
So now let me make some remarks.

01:02:08.940 --> 01:02:11.530 align:middle line:84%
So before I proceed further,
